8 offhand wepon this will happen:<br><br>every 1.8 seconds you will swing if you pass your DW roll, at the end of the swing you have a chance skill baised to swing again (da)<br><br>If your first attack rolls a hit then you do damage, second ect.<br><br>You will not have any added bonus to that damage.<br>----<br><br>So, The faster the mainhand goes the more often you apply your bonuses (Remmeber the moss covered twig debogle anyone! <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  ) and at 45-50 the mainhand bonus is large enough to warent getting a faster wepon to get it applyed over and over again.<br><br>Off hand is never effected. You always want your best ratio for the most steady damage curve you can get because there is never a damage bonus.<br><br>the WS is a great pre-45 wepon for it has an amazing ratio, but after 45 its to slow for the mainhand bonus to be applied.<br><br>Off hand I wouldnt use it either, if it could be used, it just wont attack often enough to generate taunt even with the big hits at a nice ratio  (this is debatable I know)<br><br>Hope this helps and happy tanking! <p>Hurmon Knightshade Cavaler of the 51th LoH <BR>Duthud Splat Oger Meatsheeld of the 39th eatin shorty <BR>Hurmpy TheToneDeaf Messanger of the 30th song<BR>Hungy Mystic in the making of the 7th SoW <BR></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ukilaara.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Kilaara</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 30<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/22/02 7:19:14 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1437.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.elchtom.de/Fantasy/f49.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top alig